{
  "ir_hash": "sha256:397c81ece01313ccd2e47d960a03d93ac8c9e5f8d9962bed60e6b5fb9e917352",
  "knowledges": [
    {
      "content": "真空是完全没有阻力的理想化环境：介质密度为零，唯一作用力为重力。",
      "content_hash": "11f4eaa84272f62ed04495eb05559980b85f8b540eaf40a77f765de3e3d0af68",
      "declaration_index": 0,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::vacuum",
      "label": "vacuum",
      "parameters": [],
      "type": "setting"
    },
    {
      "content": "伽利略斜面实验装置：12 腕尺长的抛光木条沟槽，衬以光滑羊皮纸，使用坚硬光滑的青铜球——摩擦和空气阻力可忽略，近似纯重力环境。",
      "content_hash": "b777bbf2981868f7bbbfe91eb651544dc86bc5851bd452c08eaacd4cb8a79570",
      "declaration_index": 1,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::inclined_plane",
      "label": "inclined_plane",
      "parameters": [],
      "type": "setting"
    },
    {
      "content": "日常经验中，较重的物体下落速度确实比较轻的物体快：石头比羽毛快，铁球比木球快。",
      "content_hash": "c9ca3cc06719af867d1cb6eff7619da6b3a53ddcb2ba4502ce4475917281e918",
      "declaration_index": 2,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::obs_daily",
      "label": "obs_daily",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Daily Observation",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在不同密度的介质中比较不同重量物体的下落：介质越稠密（如水银、水、油），轻重物体的速度差异越大；介质越稀薄（如空气），差异越小。在水银中，金是唯一能下沉的物质，其他金属和石头都浮在表面。",
      "content_hash": "f8b6c083d224b8569bfe85a3a822d3b4ad08fbf0daf88a6ed51eba10a100cfad",
      "declaration_index": 3,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::obs_media",
      "label": "obs_media",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Media Observation",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在空气中做精细实验：金球、铅球、铜球、斑岩球等重材料球从 100 腕尺高处落下，金球领先铜球不超过四指宽。",
      "content_hash": "362a5073cb13f13c502b82feecf09eb6739ed1dd6e12cc661206690b7240ee28",
      "declaration_index": 4,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::obs_air",
      "label": "obs_air",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Air Experiment",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面实验第一组：在倾角 θ₁ 下，不同重量的光滑青铜球沿抛光沟槽滚下，所经距离之比等于时间之比的平方，与球的重量无关。",
      "content_hash": "29259e1b341e348b9425860bfbaf996079280a216d21b8baea948bb350015cbe",
      "declaration_index": 5,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::obs_theta1",
      "label": "obs_theta1",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Inclined Plane θ₁",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面实验第二组：在另一倾角 θ₂ 下重复实验，结果一致确认距离 ∝ 时间²，与重量无关。实验重复整整一百次，对所有倾角均成立。",
      "content_hash": "b675fa1c1cd6bbba7c6638ab7373956c07ba7ce8258f9716b74b8c43886f84aa",
      "declaration_index": 6,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::obs_theta2",
      "label": "obs_theta2",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Inclined Plane θ₂",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "物体的下落速度与其重量成正比：一个重量是另一个两倍的物体，通过同样距离所需时间为后者的一半。即重物比轻物下落更快。",
      "content_hash": "dd1fc98769fbc9b10f0ef007a395c904883a71eb787806b666e70b31a3d02601",
      "declaration_index": 7,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::hyp_aristotle",
      "label": "hyp_aristotle",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Aristotle's Law",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "不同重量物体的下落速度差异完全由介质阻力造成——阻力是速度差异的唯一原因。阻力越大，差异越大；阻力越小，差异越小。",
      "content_hash": "c9908662b5a1a15d1cfc9db010fa030f85d521ffc38b6ec62c8e6a74f9369bb9",
      "declaration_index": 8,
      "exported": true,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::hyp_air_resistance",
      "label": "hyp_air_resistance",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Air Resistance Hypothesis",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在完全没有阻力的介质（真空）中，不同重量的物体以相同速率下落。",
      "content_hash": "42571577c94af98df3725e59beeffbd3b92ba91f4469592c85a2db462ae908a2",
      "declaration_index": 9,
      "exported": true,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::hyp_vacuum_equal",
      "label": "hyp_vacuum_equal",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Vacuum Equal Speed",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在亚里士多德定律下，将重球 H（速度 8）与轻球 L（速度 4）绑在一起，L 对 H 产生拖拽，复合体 HL 的下落速度应小于 H 单独的速度 8。",
      "content_hash": "16e36b10163b2f5c92dd7c5ae8979babe023cd3bf6e5b06b924d9b102fa56b14",
      "declaration_index": 10,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::hyp_drag",
      "label": "hyp_drag",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Tied-Ball Drag Argument",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在亚里士多德定律下，复合体 HL 的总重量大于 H 单独的重量，因此按该定律，HL 的下落速度应大于 H 单独的速度 8。",
      "content_hash": "ac14f8fbd78c3c7db9465c5ffa97b54ca86bb68d22401fa77659c62db2f5679a",
      "declaration_index": 11,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::hyp_mass",
      "label": "hyp_mass",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Tied-Ball Mass Argument",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "若物体下落速度与重量成正比是普遍规律，则在真空中也应如此：较重物体在真空中仍比较轻物体下落更快。",
      "content_hash": "22388b03ff61f4f9b09ebf7123cc75584a28a895816b736d583f75eb9cfb84a8",
      "declaration_index": 12,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::hyp_aristotle_vac",
      "label": "hyp_aristotle_vac",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Aristotle in Vacuum",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "等速假说预测：在近似无摩擦的斜面上（倾角 θ₁），不同重量的球应呈等加速，距离 ∝ 时间²，与重量无关。",
      "content_hash": "49cc786cbe776eaa86725e6a9b4b5ee2f1304e9a74ced361ba09e95462d520c0",
      "declaration_index": 13,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::pred_theta1",
      "label": "pred_theta1",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Plane Prediction θ₁",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "等速假说预测：在另一倾角（θ₂）的斜面上，同样应呈等加速，距离 ∝ 时间²，与重量无关。",
      "content_hash": "fa9032131e23d9ab146ed1bd03e09031bfac55a71944291e343faea943a7351c",
      "declaration_index": 14,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "reg:galileo_falling_bodies::pred_theta2",
      "label": "pred_theta2",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Plane Prediction θ₂",
      "type": "claim"
